

BDT Capital Partners, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 10:23 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of BDT Capital Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BDT Capital Partners, LLC is a merchant bank. It provides long-term capital to family-owned and entrepreneurial businesses. The firm’s affiliate, BDT & Company, provides strategic and advisory services to family and founder-led companies. It also co-invests. The firm seeks to invest in North America. It prefers to take a majority stake. BDT Capital Partners, LLC was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Chicago, Illinois.


401 North MichiganSuite 3100Chicago, IL 60611United StatesFounded in 2009



Phone: 312-660-7311








