BDT Capital Partners LLC


                  BDT Capital Partners focuses on investing capital and providing advice to family-owned and entrepreneurial companies. The firm seeks to invest alongside best-in-class and enduring family businesses with strong management teams.                





 Boards & Committees



Corporate Boards ▾




Director

                    2011 - Current                  


City Beverage-Illinois LLC

                    CITY Beverage-Illinois LLC distributes beer and alcoholic beverages. It distributes brands like Anheuser-Busch, Inbev, Crown, Guinness, and Gambrinus. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered Markham, IL.                  




Director

                    Tenure Unconfirmed                  


Weber-Stephen Products LLC

                    Weber-Stephen Products LLC manufactures charcoal, gas, electric grills and accessories. It also operates a website with grilling tips and techniques. The firm's products are sold at home centers, hardware stores, department stores, patio stores, and other retail outlets. The company was founded by George Stephen Sr. in 1952 and is headquartered Palatine, IL.                  





